S. Scott Bullock https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/S._Scott_Bullock 0 Stuart Scott Bullock (born May 7, 1956), better known as S. Scott Bullock, is an American actor, singer, voice actor and comedian, best known for performing the voice of Flapper in Dink the Little Dinosaur, Wendell in Mike, Lu and Og, Eddy in the Barnyard franchise, Thunder in Teen Titans, Captain Bones and Lens McCracken in Crashbox, Lamont in Gargoyles, and King Goobot in The Adventures of Jimmy Neutron: Boy Genius (taking over for Patrick Stewart).
